            <tr>
              <td> Mouse </td>
              <td> Select mouse button orientation and mouse acceleration speed.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Hardware Switches </td>
              <td> Set actions to specialized hardware bindings (ACPI) e.g.
