            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Touch </td>
              <td> Settings for touchpads.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="2">
                <h3>Settings</h3>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Dialogs </td>
              <td> Set options for dialog windows including if they should
                behave like normal windows and, if available, whether they
                should automatically open in Basic or Advanced mode.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="profiles.html">Profiles</a></td>
              <td>Create, delete, and switch between different Profiles.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="2">
                <h3>Launcher</h3>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="everything.html">Everything Configuration</a></td>
              <td>Configure the Run Everything program including how choices are
                sorted, view type, size, alignment, and active plugins.</td>
