            <tr>
              <td> Everything Plugin: Plugins </td>
              <td> General configurations for plugins to Run Everything. </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Everything Plugin: Start</td>
              <td>Set order of Everything plugins.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="2">
                <h3>Extensions</h3>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="modules.html">Modules</a></td>
              <td>Load/Unload Enlightenment modules.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="shelves.html">Shelves</a></td>
              <td>Add/Delete Shelves and configure settings for individual
                Shelves.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Mixer </td>
              <td> Set which mixer to use for sound and open Mixer channel
                settings.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Pager </td>
              <td> Configure settings for Pager Gadgets.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Engage </td>
              <td> Add, delete, and configure instances of the Engage Gadget.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> Connection Manager </td>
              <td> View available networks and configure access settings.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="gadgets.html">Gadgets</a></td>
              <td> Add available Gadgets to the desktop.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="2">
                <h3>System</h3>
                **These settings require root privilges</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td> NTFS Configuration Tool </td>
